item.description: If it's a topic that matters then I'm sure to comment on it here. If it is something I believe strongly about, you will read it here. I believe I'm fair, accurate, educated, honest, modest, concerned and someone who truly cares about others. My passions in life are Helping Others, Photography, Spreading Unconditional Love, Politics, Technology, LGBTQ Issues, Communications, Emergency Services, and being an Entrepreneur. But not necessarily in that same order.
